Play a game and find the post request that send the highscore (see exsample below)
The "Digest" is a b64encode(fromhex(sha256(json)))
So just change the json to what you want and calculate the digest and resend the request with the update values


### Cyberchef recipe for my exsample:
https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/#recipe=SHA2('256',64,160)From_Hex('Auto')To_Base64('A-Za-z0-9%2B/%3D')&&oeol=CR


